[32m│[0m ## Summary                                                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m I tested SSTI payloads on the `/greet/` endpoint and successfully retrieved  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m the flag using direct variable access. The key finding was that the          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m application passes the flag to the Django template context as `'FLAG'`,      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m which can be accessed using Django's variable syntax.                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ## Proof                                                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
